<tr>
<td class="" style="padding: 0.3em 0.4em 0.3em; font-weight: bold; border-top: 1px solid #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; text-align: center;"><a href="/wiki/File:Mosque02.svg" class="image"><img alt="Mosque02.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e7/Mosque02.svg/15px-Mosque02.svg.png" width="15" height="7" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Portal:Islam" title="Portal:Islam">Islam Portal</a><br />
<span style="font-weight:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Portal:Politics" title="Portal:Politics">Politics portal</a></span></td>
