ic_Group_of_Algeria" title="Armed Islamic Group of Algeria">Armed Islamic Group</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Islamic_Courts_Union" title="Islamic Courts Union">Islamic Courts Union</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Mahdi_Army" title="Mahdi Army">Mahdi Army</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Fatah_al-Islam" title="Fatah al-Islam">Fatah al-Islam</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hamas" title="Hamas">Hamas</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Hezbollah" title="Hezbollah">Hezbollah</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Mill%C3%AE_G%C3%B6r%C3%BC%C5%9F" title="Millî Görüş">Millî Görüş</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/National_Congress_(Sudan)" title="National Congress (Sudan)">National Congress (Sudan)</a></span></div>
